(1699, 660, 'Georges Gennaoui', 'Managing and Financial Director', 'georges.gennaoui@rudder.mc', '+336 7863 9953', '', 'Has established, developed, and managed, with responsibility for finance, accounting and other administrative matters, several companies trading energy products, such as oil, coal and electricity. Has performed several feasibility studies, and business plans for early-stage developments. Responsible for business development and financial management.', ''),
(1700, 660, 'Christian Gennaoui', 'Marketing & Trading Manager', 'christian.gennaoui@rudder.mc', '+336 7863 9988', '', 'Nine years experience for an international shipping group controlling dry and tanker vessels, of which eight years in operations and one year in chartering. Subsequent experience as bunker trader for a bunker trading company. Christian’s long experience acting both as a bunker end-user and bunker seller, and his understanding of both parties’ requirements and perspectives, is extremely valuable to RUDDER. Responsible for business development and for managing relationships with customers and suppliers.', ''),
(1701, 660, 'Dario Cacace', 'Trading & Operations Manager', 'dario.cacace@rudder.mc', '+336 7863 9949', '', 'Long and broad experience in the Italian integrated oil group ERG, where he acquired skills in domestic downstream marketing, logistics, procurement of crude and fuel oil, tanker chartering, and sale of refined oil product cargoes. Following his experience at ERG, was responsible for marketing fuel oil, and steam coal to, and developing industrial projects for, electric utilities. Responsible for business development, for managing relationships with suppliers, and for cargo market trading.', ''),
(1702, 660, 'Rachel Lachat', 'Senior Bunker Trader', 'rachel.lachat@rudder.mc', ' +33 6 8086 7417', '', 'Since 2012, Rachel\'s communication skills and ability to adapt have allowed her to shift her career path to the bunker industry. Acting as a Bunker Buyer for numerous fleets and simultaneously as a Bunker Trader for important 3rd party clients, she has acquired the knowledge of the industry\'s operations in detail. Rachel\'s aptitude allows her to cover both supply and customer sides of the business; and on a daily basis handles the bunker requests, worldwide, at any given time.', ''),
(1703, 660, 'Simone Marino', 'Senior Bunker Trader', 'simone.marino@rudder.mc', '+33 640 62 1819', '', 'Ten years experience in the shipping industry covering responsibilities through ship operations, sales & purchases, freight derivative brokerage. After a decade of experience with Ship Owners and Trading Commodity Houses, Simone has joined Rudder since 2015 and follows the worldwide bunker trading.', ''),
(1704, 660, 'Risa Fukushima', 'Senior Bunker Trader', 'risa.fukushima@rudder.mc', '+41 75 434 8643', '', 'Risa started her shipping career in Singapore and has a long experience in the industry. She started her career in ship broking followed by operations which then led her to join the bunker industry in 2011. Focusing on sales and marketing, she has established building an international portfolio and currently following worldwide bunker trading and operations.', ''),
(1705, 660, 'Emilio Naddeo', 'Senior Bunker Trader', 'emilio.naddeo@rudder.mc', '+336 7863 9951', '', 'Experience in the operations department of an international shipping group, and five years as a bunker trader for a bunker fuel trading house, where he was also responsible for administration and accounting. Responsible for daily trading and operations.', ''),
(1706, 660, 'Stelios Makris', 'Group Credit Risk Manager', ' stelios.makris@rudder.mc', '+336 4391 4017', '', 'Through his work as shipping credit risk analyst in the last 14 years both in the UK as well as in Greece for Lloyd\'s MIU, he has performed several business risks audits to a wide network of companies in the European as well as the international shipping community. He holds a BSc in Maritime Studies and MBA in Shipping Finance and he is a member of Institute of Chartered Shipbrokers as well as of Institute of Transport & Logistics. He is responsible for credit risk management.', ''),
(1707, 660, 'Agnieszka Tison', 'Accounts & Internal Audit', 'agnieszka.tison@rudder.mc', '+377 9797 6964', '', 'Fifteen-year experience as an auditor where she was been a senior member of the auditors at KPMG in Monaco. Since November 2015 as part of our team, Agnieszka has been a strong asset and she follows all auditing, compliance and statistics requirements. Agnieszka speaks fluently five languages.', ''),
(1708, 660, 'Ineke Langeveld', 'Accounts Payable & Receivable', 'ineke.langeveld@rudder.mc', '+336 7863 9441', '', 'Ineke has cumulated her experience in secretarial and administration works. She is in charge of the back office controlling the supplier\'s invoices and preparing the invoices to customers.', ''),
