(1973, 751, 'James Coker', 'Executive Director Finance', 'jamescoker@holabmaritimeservices.com.ng', '+234 803 309 8830', '', 'Mr. James N. Coker was born on the 26th December, 1978. He attended Port Harcourt Primary School, Port Harcourt and attended Government Comprehensive Secondary School, Borokiri, Port Harcourt, where he had his secondary education. He has a Bachelor’s degree in Mechanical Engineering from the University of Port Harcourt. He was the Managing Director of Jimco Nigeria Enterprises, a company that specialized in the supply of petroleum products. He is presently a director and an Executive Director of Finance and Admin with Holab Maritime Services Limited. Mr. James N. Coker is happily married.', ''),
(1974, 751, 'Sunny Anaughe', 'Executive Director Operations', 'sunny@holabmaritimeservices.com.ng', '+234 803 307 7575', '', 'Mr Sunny Oghenovo Anaughe JNR was born on the 21th of December 1969. He attended Federal Government College Port Harcourt between 1981 to 1986,, where he had his secondary education. He has a Bachelor’s degree in Economics (bsc) from Edo State University .1992 He has worked with the federal ministry of information as a clerk for four years. Metalworks Warien. as Procurements /purchasing manager. Formed sunkate Nigeria Limited a trading outfit company which later diversify to construction and much later to oil and gas. Have spent five years in the oil and gas from where he joined holab on June 2010 as a director Operations. He is presently Executive Director Operations in Holab Maritime Services Limited.\r\nMr Sunny Oghenovo Anaughe is happily married with three kid.', ''),
(1975, 751, 'Chidozie Umeji', 'General Manager', 'chydoh@holabmaritimeservices.com.ng', '+234 803 316 9510', '', 'Mr Kingsley Chidozie Umeji was born on 10th June 1976. He attended Sacred Heart Seminary, Port Harcourt. He later gained admission into the University of Port Harcourt to study Mechanical Engineering. He has a B.Eng in Mechanical Engineering. He started his working career with Hark Enterprises Nigeria Limited as a Site Manager. He later left for Jimco Nigeria Enterprises as the Logistics and Procurement Manager before he became the General Manager of Holab Maritime Services Limited.', ''),
(1976, 751, 'Favour Chukwuma', 'Head Accounts', 'accounts@holabmaritimeservices.com.ng', '+234 806 133 1834', '', 'Favour Chukwuma Born in Lagos hails from Imo State Schooled at Father Sadiku Primary School and City Stenographic collage Lagos. She holds Bsc in Bus Admin from Lagos State University. Worked at trending Connections As Sales Accountant from 97 to 2004 Joined Holab Maritime Services Limited 2009 as Accounts Clerk She is Presently Head of Accounts Department. She is Blessed With a daughter.', ''),
(1977, 751, 'Prince Ifeanyi Otisi', 'Bunker Manager', 'ifeanyi@holabmaritimeservices.com.ng', '+234 706 804 3191', '', 'A Nigerian citizen, Born in Lagos State, Nigeria. Have worked within the shipping industry since 2005. Joined Holab Maritime Services limited 2014 as Bunker Supervisor. Have enjoyed working with such a great team of professionals in the company. love spending his spare time with his family and friends. Enjoy travelling, playing football and meeting people. Mr Ifeanyi Otisi is Happily married and loves spending his spare time with his lovely wife.', ''),
(1978, 751, 'Lawrence Agwu', 'Operations Manager', 'lawrence@holabmaritimeservices.com.ng', '+234 802 402 5659', '', 'Mr Lawrence Agwu born on the 16th August 1975. He attended university Demonstration Primary School Port Harcourt and Akpor Grammar School, Ozuoba Port Harcourt. All in Rivers State. A B.Eng on Mechanical Engineer, from the University of Port Harcourt. Worked with Jimco Nigeria Enterprises as an operation coordinator. And joined Ajile Oil and Gas June 2005 to Feb 2009 as a Personal Assistant to the Chairman/CEO on Supply and Procurement. He Joined Holab Maritime Services Limited Oct. 2010 as operation Assistant and presently Operations Manager since 2014 till date Mr Lawrence is happily Married With a Son.', ''),
