(2349, 969, 'TAAHIR GALANT', 'Bunker Trader', 'taga@sabunker.com', '+27 76 664 4850', '', 'Efficiency in my position means being consistent in the quality of service to clients. It’s about achieving results and getting the job done. Aspiring to achieve high performance through a good work ethic.', ''),
(2350, 969, 'DANIEL BOTHMA', 'Sales Manager Oil & Gas', 'dabo@sabunker.com', '+27 72 580 2407', '', 'With 13 years’ experience in the Petrochemicals industry, Daniel has travelled extensively across Africa, dealing with Oil majors. He has traded chemicals to offshore rigs and vessels, and really understands the Oil sector and the difficulties that come with trading in Africa.', ''),
(2351, 969, 'KOEN DEN BOOGERT', 'O & G Sales and Logistics Specialist', 'kob@sabunker.com', ' +27 72 574 8248', '', 'Reliable, on-time quality service. To deliver over and above expectations and maintain that performance throughout your career. Ensuring your customer’s peace of mind knowing that his or her needs are taken care of in the best possible way that money can buy.', ''),
(2352, 969, 'CHAD CARNEY', 'O & G Bunker Trader', 'chca@sabunker.com', '+27 21 276 1227', '', 'Efficiency is when all aspects of something are functioning at optimum capacity. One of the core hindrances to efficiency is misunderstanding often due to a lack of communication.\r\n\r\nThrough the clarity of communication and understanding of the bigger picture, I aim to operate efficiently in all aspects of the job.', ''),
