(2794, 64, 'Eugenia Benvides', 'Marine Fuels Director', 'eugenia.benavides@terpel.com', '+57 31 5721 8311', 'eugenia benavides', '\"Born in Barranquilla, Colombia,  with a  bachelor’s degree in Business Administration and also has a post-graduate degree in International Business Management -Universidad Javeriana, and one in Maritime Transportation and Port Legislation in Pronaval, Colombia. \r\n\r\nSince 1984, Eugenia has worked with Colombian downstream major oil company Organización Terpel, handling various positions, such as sales assistant, marketing director, operations, sales, commercial manager and company’s legal representative prior to the merger between Terpel del Norte and Organización Terpel. For the past fifteen years, she has worked solely in the marine business being currently Director of Marine Fuels and she has been an active member of various professional and community organizations \r\n\r\nEugenia has also been a speaker at various bunker events in the world, IBIA board member and WISTA Colombia member\r\n\r\nEugenia is extremely enthusiastic and actively participate in diverse associations being her passion the bunker and maritime business.', 'rect_2BAJA.jpg'),
